               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Dǝrsāna Mikāʾel, Homiliary for the feasts of St Michael (fols.
                     3ra-105va)
 I-1) Homily by Timothy (Dumatewos), Patriarch of Alexandria for
                     the 12th of Ḫǝdār (fols. 3ra-8va); commemorative notice (fols. 8va-10va);
                     ʿarke-hymn (fol. 10va-vb); miracle (fols. 10vb-12va)
 I-2) Homily by an
                     anonymous author [for Tāḫśāś] (fols. 12va-17va); commemorative notice (fols.
                     17vb-18rb); ʿarke-hymn (fol. 18rb); miracle (fols. 18rb-19vb)
 I-3) Homily
                     [by Epiphanius, Metropolitan of Cyprus] for the 12th of Ṭǝrr (fols. 19vb-27va);
                     commemorative notice (fols. 27va-28ra); ʿarke-hymn (fol. 28ra-rb); miracle
                     (fols. 28rb-29rb)
 I-4) Homily by an anonymous author for the 12th of
                     Yakkātit (fols. 29rb-32rb); commemorative notice (fol. 32rb-vb); ʿarke-hymn
                     (fol. 32vb); miracle (fols. 32vb-34rb)
 I-5) Homily by [Severus] Patriarch
                     of Antiochia for the 12th of Maggābit (fols. 34rb-48ra); commemorative notice
                     (fol. 48ra); ʿarke-hymn (fol. 48ra-rb); miracle (fols. 48rb-50ra)
 I-6)
                     Homily by [Metropolitan Yoḥannǝs] the Orthodox for the 12th of Miyāzyā (fols.
                     50ra-54rb); commemorative notice (fol. 54rb-va); miracle (fols. 54va-57rb)
                     I-7) Homily by Yoḥannǝs, [Metropolitan] of Ethiopia for the 12th of Gǝnbot
                     (fols. 57rb-58vb); commemorative notice (fols. 58vb-59rb); ʿarke-hymn (fol.
                     59rb); miracle (fols. 59rb-61vb)
 I-8) Homily by [Yoḥannǝs], Metropolitan
                     of ʾAksum [for Sane] (fols. 61vb-67vb); commemorative notice (fols. 67vb-74ra);
                     ʿarke-hymn (fol. 74rb); miracle (fols. 74rb-76vb)
 I-9) Homily [by
                     Metropolitan Yoḥannǝs] for the 12th of Ḥamle (fols. 76vb-81ra); commemorative
                     notice (fols. 81ra -82va); miracle (fols. 82vb-83rb)
 I-10) Homily by an
                     anonymous author for the 12th of Naḥāse (fols. 83rb-85vb); miracle (fols.
                     85vb-91rb); commemorative notice (fol. 91rb-va); ʿarke-hymn (fol. 91va)
                     I-11) Homily by an anonymous author for the 12th of Maskaram (fols. 91va-95ra);
                     commemorative notice (fol. 95rb-va); ʿarke-hymn (fol. 95va); miracle (fols.
                     95va-98rb)
 I-12) Homily by an anonymous author for the 12th of Ṭǝqǝmt
                     (fols. 98rb-103ra); miracle (fols. 103ra-104vb); commemorative notice (fols.
                     104vb-105va); ʿarke-hymn (fol. 105va)</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">

                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
