                        <item xml:id="e1">
                           <desc type="findingAid">Monthly readings are indicated by the names of the
                              months crudely written in the upper margin, in a recent hand, in pen:
                              ሕዳር: <locus target="#3ra">fol. 3ra</locus> ታሕሣሥ: <locus target="#12vb">fol. 12vb</locus> ጥር: <locus target="#19vb">fol. 19vb</locus>
                              የካቲት: <locus target="#29rb">fol. 29rb</locus> መጋቢት: <locus target="#34rb">fol. 34rb</locus> ሚያዝያ: <locus target="#50ra">fol.
                                 50ra</locus> ግንቦት: <locus target="#57rb">fol. 57rb</locus> ሰኔ:
                                 <locus target="#61vb">fol. 61vb</locus> ሐምሌ: <locus target="#76vb">fol. 76vb</locus> ነሐሴ: <locus target="#83rb">fol. 83rb</locus>
                              መስከረም: <locus target="#91vb">fol. 91vb</locus> ጥቅምት: <locus target="#98rb">fol. 98rb</locus>.</desc>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e3">
                           <desc>- Spaces for rubricated names and incipits of subsections are sometimes left unfilled: e.g., fols. 54va, 75va-82vb; sometimes crudely filled in by a secondary hand (e.g., fols. 17vb, 18rb, 28rb, 76vb, 81ra, 82vb). - Erasures are marked with thin lines: e.g., fols. 4vb, 6va, 7rb, 17vb, 21ra, 23ra, 39ra, 51ra, 53va, 61rb. - Omitted letters and words inserted interlineally: e.g., fols. 5ra, 13vb, 37vb, 42ra, 50va, 53rb, 60rb, 68va, 71rb, 79ra, 93va. - Corrections written over erasures: e.g., fols. 8rb, 14vb, 22vb, 96va. - Immediate corrections are indicated with frames encircling words written erroneously: fols. 9rb, 9vb, 28vb, 38ra, 49vb, 60ra, 64ra, 82vb; in most cases, the scribe erroneously copied a word already written a line before (dittograpy). - Tämälläs-sign, indicating the place where the omitted passage, written in the upper margin belong: <locus target="#10rb">fol.  10rb</locus>. - Scribbles, writing exercises and crude drawings: fols. 1r-2v, 105vb, 106rb.</desc>
                        </item>
                     </list>
